Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.50,0:02:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.30,0:02:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是那个人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.20,0:02:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都是 真是缠人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.80,0:02:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 已经决定不受理她的委托了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.30,0:02:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天又没有回应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.50,0:02:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.60,0:02:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再试一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.90,0:02:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 今天就算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.20,0:02:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.30,0:02:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好饿哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.40,0:02:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在去吃点什么吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.60,0:02:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我在公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.70,0:02:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会儿见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.50,0:03:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是能认识地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.00,0:03:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这所公司的收益很容易就能翻一倍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.70,0:03:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不过那样的话 你就要被免职了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.60,0:03:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天是早上开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.40,0:03:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 我明天有期末考试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.50,0:03:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要开董事会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.60,0:03:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美沙里 你以为自己是靠谁才能上学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.40,0:03:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.70,0:03:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.90,0:04:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H0000FF&}高塔上的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.50,0:04:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 在线商店Dead Line是海部里穗社长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.50,0:04:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在学生时代和几个好友创办的公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.90,0:04:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然创业成员就剩下里穗社长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.30,0:04:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但凭着社长丰富的电脑知识和经营才学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.00,0:04:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅用四年就发展为这么大的公司了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.20,0:04:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是位厉害人的物啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.70,0:04:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有职员都很尊敬她的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.60,0:04:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能相信吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.20,0:04:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只用四年哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.00,0:04:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧你说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.10,0:04:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 就像我用了什么歪门邪道似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.70,0:05:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.30,0:05:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对没有那个意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.40,0:05:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是新来的兼职人员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.80,0:05:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫恩田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.20,0:05:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.20,0:05:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是社长海部里穗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.00,0:05:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照啊 恩田小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.20,0:05:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.50,0:05:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就是因为这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.60,0:05:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绿通信社的M&A的计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.70,0:05:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为股东之一的绿川先生强硬反对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.00,0:05:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前情势不容乐观
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.70,0:05:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请继续努力与其进行交涉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.50,0:05:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我认为他们怎么都不会改变想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.30,0:05:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不放弃的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.80,0:05:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神明总会降临的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.70,0:05:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止也就是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.60,0:05:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.40,0:05:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么接下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.60,0:05:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是扩充主机电脑一事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.70,0:05:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请参阅手边的资料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.20,0:05:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光通信也委托我公司扩充电脑 在各过程…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.80,0:05:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 里穗社长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.60,0:05:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于这个项目 社长是专家中的专家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.20,0:05:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就全部拜托社长您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.10,0:06:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣幸之至
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.70,0:06:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,董事会净是些蠢货
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.70,0:06:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要你来问我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.50,0:06:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女高中生样貌的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.00,0:06:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 刚才在厕所前看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.60,0:06:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 肯定是美沙里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.60,0:06:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦野美沙里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.40,0:06:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是里穗社长的远亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.20,0:06:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔会在公司看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.20,0:06:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦野美沙里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.60,0:06:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实应该是在就读高一或高二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.30,0:06:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双亲已经去世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.60,0:06:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里穗社长在照顾她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.30,0:06:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是为了学习社会经验
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.40,0:06:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而在这间公司打工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.60,0:06:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.50,0:06:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.60,0:06:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是社长的亲戚 可电脑却完全不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.60,0:06:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以虽说是打工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.20,0:06:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是打扫卫生倒茶什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.70,0:06:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就是社长一个人加班时作作陪同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.80,0:07:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.20,0:07:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有呢 里穗社长以前的男友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.20,0:07:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这个说过头了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.20,0:07:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是件不幸的消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.60,0:07:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绿川通信的原社长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.30,0:07:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现为第一大股东的绿川雷藏逝世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.50,0:07:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鄙人绿川雷藏所有的绿川通信社股份中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.50,0:07:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,75%转让给Dead Line公司里穗社长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.30,0:07:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是做过头了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.70,0:07:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.50,0:07:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 把这些输入那个老头的电脑里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.10,0:07:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伪装成是10天前写的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.20,0:07:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文件的属性和注册表会改好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.70,0:07:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 建在哪个目录下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.30,0:07:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些就交给你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.30,0:07:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于什么属性怎么样 服务器怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.30,0:07:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全无法理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.30,0:07:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不明白那些懂电脑的人的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.90,0:08:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 到时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.40,0:08:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要更加偏激
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.80,0:08:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要消除怨恨的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.80,0:08:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让对方深信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.00,0:08:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是替人所为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.30,0:08:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如小姐所估计的一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.30,0:08:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又没反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.70,0:08:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女什么的 不会根本就没有吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.70,0:08:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美沙里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.70,0:08:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过那个主页揪出那个混蛋的真面目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.70,0:08:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点小事 轻松搞定的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.00,0:08:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和偷盗新产品数据篡改帐户余额相比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.90,0:08:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.80,0:08:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想做回在商店偷窃的少女吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.20,0:08:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那个意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.70,0:08:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前天社长说过后我试过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.20,0:08:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是对方反而突破了我们的防火墙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.60,0:08:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差点入侵到我们的电脑中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.10,0:08:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 我才不管那么多呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.40,0:09:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,商店偷盗的少女啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.60,0:09:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心不下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.60,0:09:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家店是Dead Line的分公司吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.30,0:09:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我们的总公司啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.30,0:09:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前交往的女友经常在那打工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.40,0:09:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 听说那个公司只雇佣女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.00,0:09:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兼职也全部都是女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.10,0:09:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 现在是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.70,0:09:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前公司也有像我一样的男性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.60,0:09:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 公司的主力转为面向女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.40,0:09:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男性就外派到关系公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.80,0:09:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说白了就是降职
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.70,0:09:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有重回总公司的可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.00,0:09:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了 我已经不能回到总公司了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.20,0:09:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 准没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.80,0:10:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降职就是这个意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.50,0:10:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也回不去了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.60,0:10:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长 请振作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.70,0:10:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷窃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.30,0:10:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长的店应该也发生过吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.30,0:10:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 也是偶尔啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.70,0:10:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 大约一年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.80,0:10:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个奇怪的通告哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.80,0:10:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.00,0:10:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果发现店铺小偷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.80,0:10:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在送去警察前先要和社长联络
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.30,0:10:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后 我这边抓到的孩子是社长的亲戚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.10,0:10:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长的亲戚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.80,0:10:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行 忘掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.10,0:10:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我刚才没说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.20,0:10:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 怎么话说到这么一半就不说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.20,0:10:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里穗社长叫我不要说的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.00,0:11:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 你的话我也可以告诉你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.40,0:11:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各种各样的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.20,0:11:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子 在公司貌似似乎对电脑一点都不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.50,0:11:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 据那个店长说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.60,0:11:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她似乎对电脑相当在行哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.10,0:11:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅自己可以配置电脑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.20,0:11:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至还能做黑客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.50,0:11:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与此相反
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.60,0:11:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长却不会电脑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.80,0:11:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 已经知道了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.60,0:11:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看社长室中她们的对话就明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.00,0:11:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后还有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.30,0:11:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子和里穗社长之间没有亲戚关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.70,0:11:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.50,0:11:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天我调查过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.40,0:11:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便提一句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.70,0:11:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经一起开创公司的她的恋人对电脑很在行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.20,0:11:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然好像在公司发展起来之前就分手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.30,0:11:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.70,0:12:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为需要操作电脑的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.00,0:12:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后想到了利用商店小偷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.30,0:12:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不交给警察而将其作为自己的帮手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.10,0:12:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后上圈套的就是她啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.20,0:12:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 就是这样然后用不法手段逐渐将公司扩大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.80,0:12:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.70,0:12:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.80,0:12:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美沙里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.40,0:12:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才有个奇怪的男人打电话过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.20,0:12:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想要公司的秘密暴光的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.20,0:12:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要给他一亿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.10,0:12:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是黑客吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.30,0:12:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调查这事情就是你的工作吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.60,0:12:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.80,0:12:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我上班之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.80,0:13:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对要查清那人的真面目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.70,0:13:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时间就开始工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.40,0:13:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.60,0:13:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿醉真难过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.40,0:13:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是昨天拜托我的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.50,0:13:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔去上上学吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.80,0:13:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.70,0:13:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.70,0:13:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女的事就先放一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.40,0:13:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样连续熬夜下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.20,0:13:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对皮肤不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.90,0:13:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.50,0:13:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.70,0:14:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所发现的尸体是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.60,0:14:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小林徹 33岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.90,0:14:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经营电脑…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.80,0:14:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标是小林徹 33岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.80,0:14:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用什么方法就看你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.60,0:14:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽快干掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.80,0:14:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下总算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.60,0:14:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算怎样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.70,0:14:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下总算能让警察逮捕我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.90,0:14:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追究其他罪行的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.50,0:14:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死你父亲的证据也会出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.00,0:14:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父女两还真是像啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.50,0:14:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一样擅长电脑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.00,0:14:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有之后的命运也是一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.80,0:14:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的父亲也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.90,0:14:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以放过他性骚扰的事件为条件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.90,0:14:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而使唤他来帮我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.30,0:14:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然他是被冤枉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.30,0:15:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在他受不住良心责备想向警察告密时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.80,0:15:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就从这个世界上消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.00,0:15:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出这家公司费了不少劲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.40,0:15:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在这里可是机密哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.00,0:15:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦野
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.40,0:15:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 田村美沙里小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.80,0:15:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.20,0:15:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不会操作电脑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.50,0:15:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上有一种叫侦探的便利职业哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.50,0:15:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉田村后为难的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.90,0:15:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好你出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.50,0:15:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就觉得这里面有些蹊跷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.60,0:15:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是雇了侦探来调查你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.60,0:15:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷东西被抓是你故意的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.50,0:15:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了混入这个公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.10,0:16:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑客侵入也是为了抓住我的把柄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.70,0:16:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 实在是遗憾 你反被我将了一军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.40,0:16:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的行动全被看穿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.70,0:16:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有 有人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.30,0:16:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.20,0:16:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警卫刚才已被这家伙收拾掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.30,0:16:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的性命难道不值一提吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.00,0:16:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是杀一个和杀几个都一样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.00,0:16:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是这样把公司搞大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.30,0:16:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你绝对会下地狱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.70,0:16:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是几十年后的事了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.00,0:16:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生说到底就是场游戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.60,0:16:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游戏结束前享乐的人就是赢家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.50,0:16:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让她跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.10,0:16:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是有这种事 所以才想用地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.50,0:16:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人在关键时刻总是不管用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.70,0:17:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.60,0:17:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 地狱通信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.30,0:17:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 杀了海部吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.70,0:17:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.10,0:17:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你呼唤我的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.20,0:17:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.00,0:17:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阎魔爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.40,0:17:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.30,0:17:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请收下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.70,0:17:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你若真的要消除怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.40,0:17:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将这红线解开即可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.00,0:17:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开绳线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.50,0:17:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和我正式缔结了契约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.50,0:17:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怨恨的人将立刻坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.50,0:18:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是立刻吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.90,0:18:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是几十年之后吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.80,0:18:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.40,0:18:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨若已消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.40,0:18:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自身亦将付出代价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.60,0:18:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害人终害己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.40,0:18:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死后 你的灵魂将坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.00,0:18:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界才是地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.90,0:18:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要那个人还活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.70,0:18:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨 恨 已 闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.60,0:18:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解决了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.70,0:18:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少回个话啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.90,0:18:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.80,0:18:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dead Line公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.70,0:18:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了 我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.80,0:19:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健二 硬盘是这个吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.80,0:19:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的 里穗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.50,0:19:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是有原因的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.70,0:19:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死 死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.60,0:19:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里穗 你干了什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.20,0:19:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能让你们把我的人生弄得一团糟呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.70,0:19:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托你们的福我觉悟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.80,0:19:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管用什么手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.00,0:19:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都要赢得人生的游戏给所有人看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.20,0:19:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕牺牲掉所有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.10,0:19:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一个就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.80,0:19:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一个牺牲掉的就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.00,0:20:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就轮到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.40,0:20:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 社长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.00,0:20:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.90,0:20:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.00,0:20:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱的入口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.20,0:20:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说过轮到你了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.70,0:20:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷失于黑暗中的可悲之影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.60,0:20:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤害鄙视他人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.10,0:20:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉溺于罪恶的孽魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.40,0:20:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来死一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.40,0:20:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.60,0:20:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我必须屡次被杀啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.60,0:20:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是屡次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.60,0:21:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是永远啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.60,0:21:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此怨此恨 将流向地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.60,0:21:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 听说了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.00,0:21:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天被抓住的暴徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.60,0:21:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说自己杀了警卫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.60,0:21:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是警卫老伯不是生龙活虎吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.00,0:21:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.40,0:21:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人是不是在做梦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.60,0:21:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 梦幻破灭呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.40,0:21:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里穗社长对于电脑竟然一窍不通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.60,0:21:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说社长的工作全部是美沙里在做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.70,0:21:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且她今天开始住进了里穗社长用过的公寓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.90,0:21:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在跟谁说话啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.60,0:21:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在和谁说话呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.40,0:21:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也听到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.20,0:21:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.80,0:21:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样啊 白领的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.10,0:22:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是不合适啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.80,0:22:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直坐在桌子前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.70,0:22:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷失于黑暗中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.60,0:22:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了的话 一定会下地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.20,0:22:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那可是几十年后的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.90,0:22:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生说到底就是场游戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.50,0:22:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游戏结束前享乐的人就是赢家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.50,0:22:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 也是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.90,0:22:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我尽情享受这场游戏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.60,0:23:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君之怨恨 愿为消之
