Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:34.00,0:24:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.70,0:24:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安田遥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:37.40,0:24:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨他吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.30,0:24:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天 在窗口看到了这番情景
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.60,0:24:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲 好可怜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.20,0:24:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也看不下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:46.80,0:24:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿望是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.50,0:24:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那家伙流放到地狱去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.50,0:24:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨 恨 已 闻
